From 540f73abd2c65c8e1b122ed91bd433b26fef64d7 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Hans-Kristian Arntzen <post@arntzen-software.no>
Date: Mon, 26 Jan 2026 11:56:47 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 02/19] DO NOT MERGE: Implement VK_EXT_descriptor_heap and rip
 out all old paths.

Triage branch for heap bringup. Production path needs to consider DB +
heap paths together at least, which will complicate things a lot.

Some things like descriptor QA and friends are not fully implemented on
this branch either.

Some CPU optimizations are also missing like custom vtables for known
descriptor sizes.
